{
  "texts": [
    "Survey data were collected from 13 th July to 1 st September 2023.",
    "Following the initial email outreach and four subsequent reminders, 222 emails bounced back, and 142 recipients actively opted out of participating.Of those who opened the survey link, 266 respondents answered the initial questions.",
    "However, some immediately declined to continue, resulting in 236(5.5% of the emails sent) participants who started the survey and were included in the final analysis upon response.",
    "The geographical distribution and demographic data of 229 respondents are depicted in Table 1,.The United States and the United Kingdom were most prominently represented, accounting for 57 (24.9%) and 41 (17.9%) of respondents, respectively.",
    "In total, English-speaking nations (USA, UK, Canada, and Australia) accounted for 124 (54.1%) of respondents."
  ]
}